RRR.title: Clone
RRR.about:
A travers une approche minimaliste et un Drone éthéré, la musique de Clone matérialise un état latent, une altération, un vécu extra-sensoriel au contenu indescriptible.
Clone se situe quelque part aux limites d'un réel, d'un vide et d'une faille dont l'articulation engendre l'instabilité et la répétion.
Through a minimalist approach and an ethereal Drone, Clone's music materializes a latent state, an alteration, an extra-sensory experience with indescribable content.
Clone is located somewhere at the limits of a reality, a void and a fault whose articulation generates instability and repetition.
RRR.credits:
released March 11, 2020
RRR is Sébastien Bach
Artwork by Julien Von Corda
Recorded at the Blackened Room, 2009 - 2011
